{"tid":25991,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實港鐵真係完美演繹左咩叫賤格","createTime":"2016-12-06T12:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T11:36:18.000Z","uid":58089,"like":165,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b28b20a170104bd960c2d29c5062914f961f166f","tid":25991,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"年年加價都算鳩數喇, 我都明商人最重要係賺錢<br />\n但屌你老母你可唔可以有良心d咁賺錢呀?<br />\n拎埋d錢做d不切實際既野, 請埋d黃衫狗十個九個都黑口黑面hea企<br />\n查飛狗就仲仆街 屌你好心炒哂班垃圾慳返d錢減價仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n列車服務一年比一年差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行兩行又列車服務受阻搭地鐵真係會塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔撚正視下繁忙時段迫過狗既問題, 好心取消哂班老坑繁忙時段優惠啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ca68bef5b7211509ee218ffbb6561f6a6310c","tid":25991,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"有心post必回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c393d55feca1df6ece2d604a160d94e782d1a286","tid":25991,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年年加價都算鳩數喇, 我都明商人最重要係賺錢<br />\n<br />\n但屌你老母你可唔可以有良心d咁賺錢呀?<br />\n<br />\n拎埋d錢做d不切實際既野, 請埋d黃衫狗十個九個都黑口黑面hea企<br />\n<br />\n查飛狗就仲仆街 屌你好心炒哂班垃圾慳返d錢減價仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n列車服務一年比一年差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行兩行又列車服務受阻搭地鐵真係會塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔撚正視下繁忙時段迫過狗既問題, 好心取消哂班老坑繁忙時段優惠啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府根本係最大股東添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e4f658c0244bd6eaa267dff373a4b6d6017e62","tid":25991,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"未出哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚賤係又開d濕鳩線 成日諗住點cap水<br />\n擺明就想收巴士小巴皮<br />\n<br />\n最後係個廁所 我屌你老母美孚個廁所真係仲污糟過旺角公廁<br />\n你一年賺咁撚多億可唔可以整靚少少個廁所呀?<br />\n<br />\n對香港人就揸乾揸盡 帶樂器表演都唔撚比<br />\n大陸狗成個雪櫃上車又無人理<br />\n前排仲要出個深圳兒童優惠<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦狗鐵 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838c9b5993accd2d1ab0fcbc2c1d486208518a39","tid":25991,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"仲有高登仔最憎既關愛座<br />\n又話2個增至4個 其實係咪係都要同香港人過意唔去?"},{"pid":"79dfc4caef843a86a3bb3d3b624a5119014d6c3c","tid":25991,"uid":56352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"查飛狗真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e200d9bba6d916650c75f26158f9f39cb8a2313a","tid":25991,"uid":3328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>查飛狗真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到查飛狗必屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75bea31f7ef650ebd7e2e1e1e9797d85fb8e06a","tid":25991,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"而加仲識拍定廣告叫大家體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n省返啲錢減價好過啦<br />\n<br />\n關愛座又係on9<br />\n不過最多謝係啲道德撚<br />\n無道德撚個矛盾跟本唔會咁大<br />\n唔會搞到啲人怕公審而有位唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n道德撚真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478f1087f6f44d7fffe83fd48609d6e47fdd7206","tid":25991,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"我正係想佢開返大少少D冷氣"},{"pid":"ab7a0e9c8ded050311827aca842d924ff4e695c4","tid":25991,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"我諗我起碼半年無搭過呢條地蟲<br />\n<br />\n有得揀，我一定唔搭佢"},{"pid":"37a09502148c4ff808537c8ab41640a562b60483","tid":25991,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而加仲識拍定廣告叫大家體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n省返啲錢減價好過啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關愛座又係on9<br />\n<br />\n不過最多謝係啲道德撚<br />\n<br />\n無道德撚個矛盾跟本唔會咁大<br />\n<br />\n唔會搞到啲人怕公審而有位唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n道德撚真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋日朝早返工 有個拎3,4個袋既呀婆上車<br />\n同佢對望左1-2秒後 繼續坐係度玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎咁多野咁好力就唔洗坐啦呀婆<br />\n(結果由美孚到太子佢先有位坐)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f741a844a7d3f8052a152d3199b0837329a70b","tid":25991,"uid":33219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"c26a1a17ff763f81a7fe67261b99d95e0ac3c7cb","tid":25991,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而加仲識拍定廣告叫大家體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n省返啲錢減價好過啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關愛座又係on9<br />\n<br />\n不過最多謝係啲道德撚<br />\n<br />\n無道德撚個矛盾跟本唔會咁大<br />\n<br />\n唔會搞到啲人怕公審而有位唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n道德撚真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋日朝早返工 有個拎3,4個袋既呀婆上車<br />\n同佢對望左1-2秒後 繼續坐係度玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎咁多野咁好力就唔洗坐啦呀婆<br />\n(結果由美孚到太子佢先有位坐)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁好精神咁好精力洗咩讓佢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n在此呼籲唔好再讓畀小朋友坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講過好多次<br />\n一邊屌港孩在溫室成長<br />\n一邊幫手製造個溫室出來 坐車都要畀位佢坐先<br />\n真係好撚矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乖嘅小朋友都算<br />\n有啲直情企上張凳到<br />\n啲細路對鞋都唔知踩過乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要企就畀佢企返落地啦<br />\n啲老母又唔識教<br />\n真係想屌晒細路啲老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baddf5727f0c3bba3402d50920aec5b067eae3d","tid":25991,"uid":7165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"其實服務質素好呢，加價就無問題既。家下成撚日故障，又delay，又換條吊頸繩做扶手屌你老母狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成撚日懶係有回饋咁比啲小恩小惠你，乜撚野生日之星咁，然後就可以對外話比左幾十萬優惠香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你喇，全港七百幾八百萬人，你減一蚊都變七百幾八百萬喇陷家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59857c0a9bfff152923399913555505e9b3b64f6","tid":25991,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"凍少少已經熄冷氣<br />\n整毒氣室"},{"pid":"5dc929e5561f6a91a497a12af9718a4ab9a77708","tid":25991,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c279f06fc309e6d8460a9c5728b71e490bb28d99","tid":25991,"uid":7626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"印象中細個𠴱陣話搭地鐵塞車係好荒謬嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家係真正嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1493b596ef60ea2c5341b319f097182a6a4edd","tid":25991,"uid":11171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"